<header>CONTACTS US</header>

<h3>Leave us a comment if you have any questions, <br>
  have an inquiry regarding a service or want to leave us a review!<br>
  We would love to hear from you even if its just to say HI!<br></h3>

<h4>If you have an inquiry, please include the following in your inquiry.</h4>

<ol>
<li>Your name</li>
<li>Your contact information</li>
<li>Also be as specific as possible with your inquiry</li>
</ol>

<h4>&hearts; Can't wait to hear from you beautiful! &hearts;</h4>

<h4><a href="/comments/new">Contact form</a></h4>


<% @comments.each do |comment| %>
<div class="comment">

<p><%= comment.body %></p>
<div class="btn">
<%= link_to "Edit", edit_comment_path(comment), class: "button" %>
<%= form_for comment, method: :delete do |f|  %>
<% f.submit "Delete"%>
<% end %>
</div>
</div>
<% end %>
